會有comfort zone<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵得三皮野，一個濕9 ARE都多過佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bf9638ea636b34b31376b8ff6170631898bea6","tid":2120760,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a77d616e9ee845259fbcc11ef80b523da35e1bc0","tid":2120760,"uid":360266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"478bf82f127131a656dab1c15123687f424c2aeb","tid":2120760,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:35:19.000Z","msg":"見工人勞損　自問「自己可以幫到佢哋咩」<br />\n<br />\n伍凱瑤坦言「工程師人工不錯」，剛從香港大學土木工程工學學士畢業，就順利從事土木工程工作，並參與政府大型基建工程。這份工<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">做了3年後，月入達到逾3萬元</span></span>，令同樣從事土木工程行業的伍凱瑤爸爸感到驕傲。<br />\n<br />\n面對工程工作，伍凱瑤看到的不只是工程材料及賬目，更是工作中的人。在地盤工作時，伍凱瑤常常見到工人因長期工作而勞損，內心自問「自己可以幫到佢哋咩」。平時學習瑜伽的凱瑤，開始思考是否能夠利用自己的瑜伽知識，幫助他人紓緩痛症。但專業的治療，始終與瑜伽有別，伍凱瑤的內心亦留下了問號。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:26:16.000Z","msg":"工程=狗，點會有comfort zone<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵得三皮野，一個濕9 ARE都多過佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"工程師去外國好食香<br />\n聽其他ching係咁講"},{"pid":"d8222430b0f64f843188d5b922e7563d4bba447c","tid":2120760,"uid":129138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}